OL,7,F"There are no cast-iron guarantees
OL,8,Fthis can't happen again"
OL,10,FThe NHS trust facing criticism for its
OL,11,Ftreatment of the man behind the
OL,12,FNottingham attacks says it can't
OL,13,Fguarantee that a similar incident
OL,14,Fwon't happen again.
OL,16,FSenior trust leaders at
OL,17,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,18,FFoundation trust told a meeting at the
OL,19,FCounty Council's health committee they
OL,20,Fwere learning from past errors and
OL,21,Fapologised for mistakes that were made.
