OL,7,FJan Sensier, Executive Director of
OL,8,FPartnerships and Strategy at the trust
OL,9,Fsaid "there are no cast-iron
OL,10,Fguarantees that this can't happen
OL,11,Fagain but mistakes were made and we
OL,12,Fare working to rectify these."
OL,14,FValdo Calocane killed three people,
OL,15,Fstudents Barnaby Webber, Grace O'
OL,16,FMalley-Kumar and school caretaker Ian
OL,17,FCoates after stabbing them to death in
OL,18,FNottingham on 13 June 2023.
