OL,7,FHe also seriously injured three other
OL,8,Fpeople after driving into them with a
OL,9,Fvan in the early hours of the morning.
OL,11,FCalocane was under the care of the
OL,12,Ftrust whilst being treated for
OL,13,Fparanoid schizophrenia between May
OL,14,F2020 and September 2022.
OL,16,FHe was sentenced to an indefinite
OL,17,Fhospital order in January, after
OL,18,Fadmitting manslaughter on the grounds
OL,19,Fof diminished responsibility.
