OL,7,FThe Nottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust said they are "doing
OL,9,Feverything possible" to minimise the
OL,10,Frisk of a similar incident and are
OL,11,Fworking to tackle the "systematic
OL,12,Ffailures" that caused the attacks to
OL,13,Fhappen.
OL,15,FThe trust also says work is being done
OL,16,Fon how patients are discharged,
OL,17,Fparticularly those in communities with
OL,18,Fa similar profile to Calocane.
