OL,7,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,8,Freport released in August found that
OL,9,Fthe killer's risk was "not managed
OL,10,Fwell" and that concerns raised by the
OL,11,Fkiller's family were "not consistently
OL,12,Facted on".
OL,14,FIt also found that the risk
OL,15,Fassessments did not "make explicit the
OL,16,Fserious nature" that Calocane posed.
